OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FAfghan refugees take UK to 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fcourt over school move     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A group of Afghan families brought to  
OL,6, London after the Taliban took power are
OL,7, taking the government to court because 
OL,8, a subsequent move north meant their    
OL,9, children had to leave a local school   
OL,10, during their GCSE studies.             
OL,12,FFour families were moved from a London 
OL,13,Fhotel to one in northern England.      
OL,15,FA lack of school places near their new 
OL,16,Ftemporary home has since set back the  
OL,17,Fteenagers' education, the families say.
OL,19,FThe Home Office said it was trying to  
OL,20,Ffind permanent homes for Afghans.      
